# Introduction

The objective of this study is to investigate the relationship between various socio-demographic features, past marketing experiences,
and the likelihood of successful customer deposit subscription in a Portuguese bank.

# Data Description

In this section, the data of the Portuguese retail bank collected between May 2008 and November 2010 was described.
It is publicly available in the UCI Machine Learning Repository [https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/bank+marketing#].

